.TH "libnvme_strerror" 9 "libnvme_strerror" "April 2026" "libnvme API manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
libnvme_strerror \- Returns string describing nvme errors and errno
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "const char *" libnvme_strerror
.BI "(int err "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "err" 12
Returned error codes from all libnvme functions
.SH "RETURN"
String representation of either the nvme connect error codes
(positive values) or errno string (negative values)
